<plot>In this adaption of an ancient Mic Mac legend, the land is in the grip of a deep and deadly winter that threatens the people. The great hero, Glouscap, vows to find the source of this dangerous climate. Finding the responsible entity, Winter, and unable to defeat him, Glouscap must search for a way to restore the land.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?521072</url></doc>
